| % Schools with | 2010 | 2012 | 2014 | 2016 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| School Management Committee (SMC) registered | 94.5 | 96.2 | 97.1 | 97.5 |
| SMC meeting held in last year | 68.5 | 72.3 | 75.4 | 78.2 |
| School Development Plan (SDP) prepared | 45.2 | 52.1 | 60.3 | 65.8 |
| SDP implemented | 28.4 | 35.6 | 42.1 | 48.5 |
| School Fund account maintained | 32.1 | 40.5 | 55.2 | 62.4 |
| School Fund utilized for school development | 18.5 | 25.3 | 38.7 | 45.2 |
| Parent-Teacher Association (PTA) active | 42.3 | 48.5 | 52.1 | 55.8 |

